text.tspan: Machines Create New VM Dialog: Storage — April 2019

flowRoot.flowPara: Path to ISO file on host's file system
By default, Cockpit manages storage and creates a volume name based on the VM's name.
It's possible to select "No Storage" or a volume pool.
Different options will change what is shown immedately after: Size for a new volume, volume name selector for a storage pool, or nothing for "No Storage".
Path to ISO file on host's file system
A storage pool is selected, so the volume selector appears.
